RTS Futures Fall at Start of Trading, Market Vectors Drops

-- B y   H a l i a   P a v l i v a
-- 
2011-07-08T15:17:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/rts-futures-fall-at-start-of-trading-market-vectors-drops.html
Russia’s RTS stock-index futures
retreated 0.2 percent at 11:05 a.m. in  New York .  Contracts on OAO Rosneft, the country’s biggest oil
producer, decreased 0.2 percent and agreements on OAO Lukoil,
the second-largest, dropped 0.1 percent. Agreements on OAO
Gazprom, the world’s largest gas producer, sank 0.5 percent.  The Market Vectors Russia ETF, a U.S.-traded fund that
holds Russian shares, lost 1.8 percent. The American depositary
receipts of Lukoil slid 1.3 percent, while ADRs of Gazprom
declined 2.5 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Halia Pavliva in New York at 
